衛隊員を志す若者。\r\n当初は挫折したカフカを冷淡な目で見ていたが、その人柄に触れて敬意を抱くようになる。","relation":"主角","actors":[],"type":1,"id":126890},{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/a0/4b/126892_crt_C68JZ.jpg?r=1705209549","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/a0/4b/126892_crt_C68JZ.jpg?r=1705209549","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/a0/4b/126892_crt_C68JZ.jpg?r=1705209549","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/a0/4b/126892_crt_C68JZ.jpg?r=1705209549"},"name":"四ノ宮キコル","summary":"海外の討伐大学を飛び級で卒業した、史上最高の逸材と謳われる超エリートで、日本防衛隊長官・四ノ宮功の一人娘。\r\n並外れたセンスで入隊前から小隊長レベルの強さを誇る。","relation":"主角","actors":[],"type":1,"id":126892},{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/6a/64/126977_crt_um0j2.jpg?r=1705209561","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/6a/64/126977_crt_um0j2.jpg?r=1705209561","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/6a/64/126977_crt_um0j2.jpg?r=1705209561","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/6a/64/126977_crt_um0j2.jpg?r=1705209561"},"name":"保科宗四郎","summary":"日本防衛隊第3部隊副隊長。室町時代から続く怪獣討伐の家系。\r\n刀のスペシャリストで、小型～中型の怪獣討伐においては隊長の亜白ミナをも上回る実力を持つ。","relation":"配角","actors":[],"type":1,"id":126977},{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/8c/96/150759_crt_55Jpe.jpg?r=1705208804","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/8c/96/150759_crt_55Jpe.jpg?r=1705208804","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/8c/96/150759_crt_55Jpe.jpg?r=1705208804","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/8c/96/150759_crt_55Jpe.jpg?r=1705208804"},"name":"古橋伊春","summary":"八王子討伐高専を首席で卒業した実力派。負けず嫌いで粗野な言動も目立つが、実は情に厚いムードメーカー。","relation":"配角","actors":[],"type":1,"id":150759},{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/04/9e/150760_crt_BDH90.jpg?r=1705209110","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/04/9e/150760_crt_BDH90.jpg?r=1705209110","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/04/9e/150760_crt_BDH90.jpg?r=1705209110","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/04/9e/150760_crt_BDH90.jpg?r=1705209110"},"name":"出雲ハルイチ","summary":"対怪獣兵器メーカーの国内最大手である出雲テックスの御曹司であり、東京討伐大学を首席卒業した文武